text: Erist of todanbrigge of þare muchel dich on mordrancombe.
Of boreswelle on þan merkeden ok to feger ok þanen on þinaswelle of Ineswelle on Worhanan berghe.
Of Wolfpole endlang stremes on schippeburg westward on harenapildorewei þere he out lit þanen on merestan.
Of þan stone endlang mereweies to likan trowe.
Þanen est lang dich to redwines thorne.
Of þan pille on berleighe mideward þanen endlang hagen on petanberberwe þanen on þa stanenpile of þere stanenpile eft on todanberghe on the muchel dich.
